			"result": "1. Management teams carry out and    improve key management activities such as surveillance, biomonitoring, sensitization and local development around the protected areas to contribute to effective conservation of key species and biodiversity.\r\n2. Management teams are well trained and fully equipped to shield the protected areas from intruders and illegal activities."
