			"result": "1. Comprehensive management plans and their implementation for newly created protected areas and national parks result in increased biodiversity protection \r\n2. The protected area network of the Tai-Sapo complex is reinforced with Grebo and Grand Kru-River Gee becoming operational National Parks\r\n3. Improved potential of meeting up with CBD quest to conserve 10% of Liberian land space"
